snippet.textDisplay:
Hayley, I've admired you since I was 15 years old. I still do. You're a brave person for opening your heart in a song.
In a world that is hypocritical and false, you are a positive influence. You tell your truth and inspire others to tell their story and heal. Thanks for that. Thank you for having accompanied me for so many years with your music. 💜
